yue or yueh ( yüeh )   may refer to :   locations guangdong , abbreviated 粵 yuè , a province of china yue nan ( chinese : 越南 ) or vietnam zhejiang , informally abbreviated 越 yuè , a province of china   language yue chinese , a branch of chinese , spoken primarily in and around guangdong cantonese , a dialect of yue chinese , spoken in guangzhou , hong kong and macau   groups baiyue , a collection of ancient peoples in coastal southern china .

